# flan-t5-cbp-lkg-corpus-mlm-small

[Flan-T5-small](https://huggingface.co/google/flan-t5-small) pre-trained over the corpus used in [Dhani et al., 2022](https://arxiv.org/abs/2107.04771) using the span masking MLM objective.
